WWW::BookBot version 0.10
========================

Bot to fetch web e-texts with catalog, books and chapters.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	Encode
	File::Basename
	File::Spec::Functions
	File::Path
	Fcntl
	LWP::UserAgent
	HTTP::Request::Common
	HTTP::Response
	HTTP::Cookies
	HTTP::Date
	URI
	Carp
	Data::Dumper
	POSIX
	Getopt::Long

WARNING

WWW::BookBot is in pre-alpha stage. Interface may be changed latter.
More documents are required to support extended development.

BUGS, REQUESTS, COMMENTS

Please report any requests, suggestions or bugs via
http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=WWW-BookBot

